Françoise Fabian https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fran%C3%A7oise_Fabian 0 Michèle Cortes de Leone y Fabianera, better known as her stage name Françoise Fabian (French: [fabjɑ̃]; born 10 May 1933), is a French film actress. She has appeared in more than 80 films since 1956.
